<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Document</title>
    <link type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" href="Approve.css" />

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lexend&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>
  <body class="page">
    <div class="logo">
      <img src="/Images/logo1.png" alt="logo" height="50px" width="100px" />
    </div>

    <div class="checkmark">
      <img src="/Images/checkmark.png" alt="logo" height="50px" width="50px" />
    </div>

    <h1>Your Property has been Approved!</h1>
    <p class="name">{{user}}</p>

    <p class="content">
      I am pleased to inform you that your property has been approved by our
      administration team and has been added to our CRM (Customer Relationship
      Management) system. Congratulations on this achievement!
      <br />
      <br />
      Your property's details will now be visible to our network of clients who
      are looking for properties that match their requirements. We will continue
      to advertise your property to potential [renters/buyers] and keep you
      informed of any developments.
    </p>

    <div class="property-details">
      <div>
        <img src="{{image}}" height="140px" width="200px" />
      </div>
      <div class="details">
        <div class="property-title">{{title}}</div>
        <div class="detproperty">
          <div class="propertydet">Bedrooms</div>
          {{bedrooms}}
        </div>
        <div class="detproperty">
          <div class="propertydet">Bathrooms</div>
          {{bathrooms}}
        </div>
        <div class="detproperty">
          <div class="propertydet">Sqrts</div>
          {{total_size}}
        </div>

        <div class="link">
          <a href="">view details</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="content">
      Please feel free to contact us if you have any questions or concerns.
    </p>

    <p>Best Regards <br /><strong>Team CRM Pixl </strong></p>
    <div class="social-logo">
      <img src="/Images/sociallogo.png" height="70px" width="140px" />
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
